1
00:00:05,708 --> 00:00:08,404
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,477 --> 00:00:12,345
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,415 --> 00:00:16,408
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,752 --> 00:00:19,243
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,322 --> 00:00:23,383
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,459 --> 00:00:27,418
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,898 --> 00:00:33,631
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,337 --> 00:00:37,306
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,742 --> 00:00:41,835
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,578 --> 00:00:43,875
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,213 --> 00:00:46,773
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,824 --> 00:01:00,194
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,396 --> 00:01:01,556
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,630 --> 00:01:05,430
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,768 --> 00:01:10,967
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,571
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,641 --> 00:01:14,040
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,110 --> 00:01:20,379
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:33,012 --> 00:01:37,711
We now start the second test
of the Chunin Exam!

20
00:01:41,721 --> 00:01:42,710
Look for the brats!

21
00:01:43,256 --> 00:01:44,518
Those three, right?

22
00:01:47,093 --> 00:01:49,425
All right! Let's go!

23
00:01:59,172 --> 00:02:03,472
Okay! First we search for that thing.
Can you do it, Hinata?

24
00:02:03,843 --> 00:02:04,537
Yes.

25
00:02:06,546 --> 00:02:09,538
Slow down, Lee! We just started.

26
00:02:10,250 --> 00:02:12,343
I know. But...

27
00:02:13,887 --> 00:02:15,218
I can't stay still!

28
00:02:15,622 --> 00:02:17,886
Who knows what kind of
powerful foe is waiting for us?!

29
00:02:18,591 --> 00:02:21,424
As you already understand,
we have only one target!

30
00:02:28,735 --> 00:02:30,566
It sounds like they've already started.

31
00:02:32,338 --> 00:02:35,171
Huh? That was someone's
scream just now, right?

32
00:02:39,612 --> 00:02:42,206
I-I'm kinda getting nervous.

33
00:02:42,715 --> 00:02:46,708
I-It was nothing, Sakura. Believe it!

34
00:02:49,355 --> 00:02:51,653
I-I have to pee.

35
00:02:51,891 --> 00:02:53,859
Y-You... Fool!

36
00:02:54,327 --> 00:02:56,955
What are you doing in front of a lady!

37
00:02:57,197 --> 00:02:58,459
Go to the grass!

38
00:02:59,799 --> 00:03:05,396
<i>Eat or be Eaten. Panic in the Forest</i>

39
00:03:10,043 --> 00:03:14,309
Oh! Ohhh!

40
00:03:16,316 --> 00:03:19,376
Aaah... that was a lot!

41
00:03:19,819 --> 00:03:21,218
Feels much better!

42
00:03:21,454 --> 00:03:26,255
C'mon Naruto! I told you not to say
things like that in front of a lady!

43
00:03:29,295 --> 00:03:29,989
What?!

44
00:03:33,933 --> 00:03:35,161
S-Sasuke...

45
00:03:35,502 --> 00:03:37,697
no matter what,
you don't have to go that far.

46
00:03:39,906 --> 00:03:42,431
W-What was that for?

47
00:03:43,309 --> 00:03:44,571
Where's the real Naruto?!

48
00:03:45,078 --> 00:03:45,544
Huh?

49
00:03:47,914 --> 00:03:50,075
I don't know what the heck
you're talking about!

50
00:03:50,250 --> 00:03:53,947
What happened to the scratch
you got earlier from the Proctor?!

51
00:03:54,420 --> 00:03:58,254
And... your Shuriken holster
is on your left leg.

52
00:03:58,825 --> 00:04:00,452
That guy's right handed.

53
00:04:02,862 --> 00:04:07,196
You're worse at transformation
than Naruto, you phony!

54
00:04:07,901 --> 00:04:10,961
Unlucky me! In that case...

55
00:04:12,705 --> 00:04:14,673
Which one of you got the scroll?!

56
00:04:15,308 --> 00:04:16,969
Since things have come to this,
I'll resort to force!

57
00:04:19,612 --> 00:04:21,671
Fire Style:
Phoenix. Flower Jutsu!

58
00:04:27,987 --> 00:04:30,217
Heeeey! Sasuke!

59
00:04:30,456 --> 00:04:32,287
<i>You've got to be kidding, loser.</i>

60
00:04:33,226 --> 00:04:33,749
All right!

61
00:04:33,993 --> 00:04:36,154
I caught you off guard! Lucky!

62
00:04:38,531 --> 00:04:39,327
Paper Bomb!

63
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:47,901
This is lucky!

64
00:04:47,974 --> 00:04:51,466
I'll kill you if you move!
Calmly hand over the scroll!

65
00:04:52,645 --> 00:04:53,441
Sasuke!

66
00:05:00,853 --> 00:05:01,911
I won't let you get away!

67
00:05:02,622 --> 00:05:04,988
<i>Y-You're always late Naruto!</i>

68
00:05:07,860 --> 00:05:09,293
<i>Absorption with my Chakra.</i>

69
00:05:24,310 --> 00:05:25,174
Sasuke...

70
00:05:25,645 --> 00:05:27,135
Don't just stand there, Sakura!

71
00:05:27,413 --> 00:05:29,040
No guarantee this guy's alone!

72
00:05:30,149 --> 00:05:30,945
Got it?!

73
00:05:31,017 --> 00:05:32,985
If you let your guard down
you'll really get killed...

74
00:05:35,321 --> 00:05:39,018
It's unlucky! I came on my own
to conceal my presence,

75
00:05:39,092 --> 00:05:40,559
but that became my enemy...

76
00:05:46,866 --> 00:05:47,662
<i>He got away, huh?</i>

77
00:05:54,807 --> 00:05:56,866
If there's an instance that
we become separated,

78
00:05:57,210 --> 00:05:59,440
don't trust him if he looks
like your teammate.

79
00:06:00,747 --> 00:06:01,839
Just like now there's a possibility

80
00:06:01,914 --> 00:06:04,405
that an enemy will transform
to get close to us!

81
00:06:05,018 --> 00:06:07,213
- Yeah.
- So what do we do?

82
00:06:08,488 --> 00:06:09,853
We'll decide on a password.

83
00:06:10,289 --> 00:06:12,189
Password?

84
00:06:12,859 --> 00:06:18,320
Listen, if the password is incorrect,
no matter what he looks like...

85
00:06:19,198 --> 00:06:20,563
presume he is an enemy!

86
00:06:21,834 --> 00:06:24,530
I'll only say it once, so listen closely.

87
00:06:25,505 --> 00:06:27,598
You ask,
Ninja song, "Ninja Chance."

88
00:06:28,341 --> 00:06:29,831
And the answer is this:

89
00:06:30,977 --> 00:06:33,502
"The chance to sneak up when a large
number of enemies are making a scene.

90
00:06:34,113 --> 00:06:36,479
"The quiet place has no secret hideout.

91
00:06:37,116 --> 00:06:40,142
"It is important for a Shinobi
to know the right time.

92
00:06:40,620 --> 00:06:43,248
"The time when an enemy is tired
and drops his guard."

93
00:06:43,723 --> 00:06:44,485
That's it.

94
00:06:45,258 --> 00:06:46,054
Okay!

95
00:06:48,027 --> 00:06:50,120
Could you say it again?

96
00:06:50,697 --> 00:06:51,356
Huh?!

97
00:06:51,764 --> 00:06:53,356
I told you I'd only say it once.

98
00:06:53,933 --> 00:06:56,561
Could it be that you couldn't memorize it?

99
00:06:57,103 --> 00:06:58,661
- You fool!
- Huh?!

100
00:06:59,072 --> 00:07:00,630
I got it right away!

101
00:07:00,707 --> 00:07:03,938
I-I memorized it perfectly!

102
00:07:04,110 --> 00:07:08,547
I thought just in case,
I'd listen one more time...

103
00:07:08,681 --> 00:07:10,478
I'll carry the scroll!

104
00:07:11,584 --> 00:07:13,017
Hey, wait Sasuke.

105
00:07:13,186 --> 00:07:14,118
Ouch!

106
00:07:18,024 --> 00:07:18,922
What is it?

107
00:07:28,534 --> 00:07:29,364
A new enemy?!

108
00:07:38,377 --> 00:07:41,642
You guys go play around...

109
00:07:42,882 --> 00:07:44,941
I'll go alone...

110
00:07:57,930 --> 00:07:58,692
Sakura!

111
00:07:59,098 --> 00:08:00,065
Sasuke!

112
00:08:00,433 --> 00:08:01,263
Don't come closer!

113
00:08:01,567 --> 00:08:03,057
First the password...

114
00:08:03,669 --> 00:08:05,068
Ninja song, "Ninja Chance!"

115
00:08:05,404 --> 00:08:06,598
Ah! Umm...

116
00:08:07,039 --> 00:08:09,871
The chance to sneak up where a large
number of enemies are making a scene.

117
00:08:10,143 --> 00:08:12,043
The quiet place has no secret hideout.

118
00:08:12,712 --> 00:08:15,579
It is important for a Shinobi
to know the right time.

119
00:08:15,982 --> 00:08:18,007
The time when an enemy is tired
and drops his guard.

120
00:08:18,885 --> 00:08:19,681
Good.

121
00:08:19,986 --> 00:08:21,681
Owwww!

122
00:08:22,088 --> 00:08:23,953
Hey everyone, are you okay?

123
00:08:24,056 --> 00:08:25,489
Naruto, wait!

124
00:08:26,192 --> 00:08:26,851
The password...

125
00:08:27,426 --> 00:08:29,018
I know...

126
00:08:29,495 --> 00:08:32,486
The chance to sneak up where a large
number of enemies are making a scene.

127
00:08:32,498 --> 00:08:34,762
The quiet place has no
secret hideout.

128
00:08:35,101 --> 00:08:38,332
It is important for a Shinobi
to know the right time.

129
00:08:38,471 --> 00:08:40,939
The time when an enemy
is tired and drops his guard.

130
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:46,000
- What?!
- Huh?!

131
00:08:47,246 --> 00:08:49,009
What are you doing?!

132
00:08:49,916 --> 00:08:52,350
This time it's someone who
can dodge my attack, huh?

133
00:08:52,785 --> 00:08:54,776
What are you saying, Sasuke?

134
00:08:55,521 --> 00:08:57,853
Naruto just said
the password properly.

135
00:08:58,191 --> 00:08:59,852
He was able to say it,
that's the problem!

136
00:09:00,226 --> 00:09:01,625
- Huh?!
- Wha?

137
00:09:02,795 --> 00:09:06,822
Do you really think that guy can
remember a password that long?

138
00:09:06,933 --> 00:09:07,865
Oh!

139
00:09:08,668 --> 00:09:11,228
If we asked the normal Naruto
what the password is,

140
00:09:11,737 --> 00:09:14,729
what do you think he'd say?

141
00:09:15,908 --> 00:09:17,705
"Sorry. I've forgotten it."

142
00:09:19,278 --> 00:09:22,270
Besides, his movements when
he avoided my attack...

143
00:09:22,515 --> 00:09:25,279
It was clearly different
from Naruto's!

144
00:09:26,352 --> 00:09:30,118
Show your true self already,
fake one!

145
00:09:36,462 --> 00:09:38,054
That's how it is, huh...

146
00:09:44,570 --> 00:09:47,767
But if you knew he would forget it,

147
00:09:49,775 --> 00:09:53,336
why didn't you make
the password shorter?

148
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:55,609
I knew that you were
underground

149
00:09:55,882 --> 00:09:59,784
eavesdropping on
our conversation.

150
00:10:00,419 --> 00:10:03,286
So I chose that password on purpose.

151
00:10:06,292 --> 00:10:10,251
Oh really. So you're not tired
or letting your guard down.

152
00:10:11,530 --> 00:10:14,294
This will be more fun than I thought.

153
00:10:18,004 --> 00:10:20,495
<i>This person's... too creepy!</i>

154
00:10:21,507 --> 00:10:24,374
<i>And where's Naruto?</i>

155
00:10:29,415 --> 00:10:30,439
Huh?

156
00:10:30,950 --> 00:10:32,474
Owww

157
00:10:34,253 --> 00:10:36,813
And heave!

158
00:10:37,423 --> 00:10:41,189
Huh? Where are Sakura
and that Sasuke?

159
00:10:44,297 --> 00:10:47,528
H-Huge!

160
00:10:49,535 --> 00:10:52,595
<i>This is the first time I've seen...</i>
<i>a snake this huge!</i>

161
00:11:02,481 --> 00:11:03,175
Behind?!

162
00:11:06,652 --> 00:11:07,778
T-Tail!

163
00:11:24,170 --> 00:11:27,264
You want our Earth Scroll,
don't you?

164
00:11:27,907 --> 00:11:31,070
'Cause you have the Heaven Scroll.

165
00:11:45,458 --> 00:11:47,949
Well, let's begin...

166
00:11:50,262 --> 00:11:52,696
the battle for the Scrolls.

167
00:11:55,601 --> 00:11:56,966
Life or Death!

168
00:12:25,014 --> 00:12:25,981
<i>Genjutsu?!</i>

169
00:12:35,925 --> 00:12:37,119
<i>No, that's not it.</i>

170
00:12:38,694 --> 00:12:41,356
<i>This is simply</i>
<i>a thirst for blood.</i>

171
00:12:42,298 --> 00:12:43,458
<i>What's going on?</i>

172
00:12:44,767 --> 00:12:48,259
<i>Just looking at her eyes</i>
<i>made me think of death.</i>

173
00:12:52,275 --> 00:12:54,937
<i>Who is this... woman?!</i>

174
00:12:58,414 --> 00:13:00,575
Sa... kura?

175
00:13:09,992 --> 00:13:10,959
<i>It's no good.</i>

176
00:13:11,527 --> 00:13:13,017
<i>We have no choice but to flee here.</i>

177
00:13:15,598 --> 00:13:17,930
<i>Unless we do, the only thing</i>
<i>waiting for us is...</i>

178
00:13:20,970 --> 00:13:21,959
<i>Death!</i>

179
00:13:24,106 --> 00:13:26,836
Let me out! Hey!

180
00:13:28,044 --> 00:13:30,604
Spit... me... out!

181
00:13:33,015 --> 00:13:36,109
Damn!
It's not going to work.

182
00:13:37,420 --> 00:13:38,978
Something else...

183
00:13:39,722 --> 00:13:40,279
Oh!

184
00:13:42,225 --> 00:13:44,750
The rice ball I took for lunch!

185
00:13:46,462 --> 00:13:47,224
Huh?!

186
00:13:55,438 --> 00:13:56,234
It's dissolving!

187
00:13:56,906 --> 00:14:00,205
I'll be digested just like
that rice ball eventually...

188
00:14:03,546 --> 00:14:05,138
N-No!

189
00:14:05,815 --> 00:14:08,909
Let me out! Let me... out!

190
00:14:16,058 --> 00:14:17,889
Can't move already?

191
00:14:20,363 --> 00:14:21,159
<i>She's going to kill me!</i>

192
00:14:22,064 --> 00:14:24,726
<i>Move... move... move!</i>

193
00:14:24,934 --> 00:14:25,866
<i>Move!</i>

194
00:14:28,137 --> 00:14:30,196
<i>Move! Move!</i>

195
00:14:31,907 --> 00:14:32,999
<i>Move!</i>

196
00:14:43,119 --> 00:14:46,919
<i>Even if it's just a little...</i>
<i>Move!</i>

197
00:14:48,891 --> 00:14:52,349
What do you intend to do... with that?

198
00:14:57,233 --> 00:14:58,325
<i>I can't move!</i>

199
00:15:00,036 --> 00:15:04,439
Don't worry.
I'll end this in a second.

200
00:15:06,142 --> 00:15:08,110
You won't even have
the time to feel pain.

201
00:15:22,191 --> 00:15:24,819
I wanted you to entertain me more.

202
00:15:26,762 --> 00:15:27,626
It's too bad.

203
00:15:43,012 --> 00:15:46,607
<i>Am... I going to die here?</i>

204
00:15:50,186 --> 00:15:51,551
<i>Iruka Sensei</i>

205
00:15:55,224 --> 00:15:57,522
<i>Old Man Hokage...</i>

206
00:16:00,162 --> 00:16:01,288
<i>Konohamaru...</i>

207
00:16:05,267 --> 00:16:06,564
<i>Kakashi Sensei.</i>

208
00:16:10,206 --> 00:16:11,173
<i>Sakura.</i>

209
00:16:15,111 --> 00:16:16,043
<i>Sasuke.</i>

210
00:16:18,814 --> 00:16:22,375
<i>A lot happened between him and me.</i>

211
00:16:23,419 --> 00:16:25,649
<i>Even though we always squabbled,</i>

212
00:16:25,721 --> 00:16:30,715
<i>we cooperated and saved Kakashi Sensei</i>
<i>in that encounter with Zabuz a.</i>

213
00:16:33,129 --> 00:16:35,859
<i>During our Chakra training in forest,</i>

214
00:16:36,399 --> 00:16:40,392
<i>we competed each other and</i>
<i>practiced climbing up trees.</i>

215
00:16:44,039 --> 00:16:47,008
<i>That's it! I haven't...</i>

216
00:16:47,376 --> 00:16:49,606
<i>settled things with him yet!</i>

217
00:16:51,814 --> 00:16:52,906
- <i>More rice!</i>
- <i>More rice!</i>

218
00:16:58,454 --> 00:17:01,014
<i>If this creature doesn't want to</i>
<i>spit me out...</i>

219
00:17:01,590 --> 00:17:04,957
<i>I'll make it to do so at any cost!</i>

220
00:17:19,775 --> 00:17:21,140
I see.

221
00:17:42,998 --> 00:17:44,056
Sasuke!

222
00:17:47,670 --> 00:17:50,036
<i>He wounded himself</i>
<i>at the last moment...</i>

223
00:17:53,909 --> 00:17:58,005
<i>Move. Move. Move.</i>
<i>Move!</i>

224
00:18:03,819 --> 00:18:05,252
<i>Move!</i>

225
00:18:16,031 --> 00:18:18,693
<i>He wiped out the fear with pain.</i>

226
00:18:21,971 --> 00:18:24,940
<i>As expected,</i>
<i>he's not the average prey.</i>

227
00:18:27,009 --> 00:18:28,601
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

228
00:18:38,687 --> 00:18:41,781
I... am a Shinobi who
will become Hokage!

229
00:18:42,424 --> 00:18:46,053
I won't put up with being
snake dung in this place!

230
00:18:56,238 --> 00:18:57,227
Sasuke.

231
00:18:57,873 --> 00:18:58,805
Are you okay?

232
00:19:00,943 --> 00:19:04,572
<i>If we don't flee in a hurry,</i>
<i>we'll be discovered here, too.</i>

233
00:19:05,881 --> 00:19:06,813
<i>How do we flee?</i>

234
00:19:07,049 --> 00:19:08,311
<i>How should we escape?</i>

235
00:19:09,785 --> 00:19:12,686
<i>I've never seen Sasuke...</i>

236
00:19:14,023 --> 00:19:15,217
<i>so worked up.</i>

237
00:19:22,631 --> 00:19:23,859
Sasuke, a snake!

238
00:19:28,203 --> 00:19:32,071
Shoot! I was too shaken up
to notice the snake!

239
00:19:43,953 --> 00:19:45,352
Don't come near me!

240
00:20:11,113 --> 00:20:14,048
Don't lower your guard,
not even for a moment...

241
00:20:16,685 --> 00:20:21,850
A prey must always stay tense
and try to flee desperately...

242
00:20:23,859 --> 00:20:25,850
before a predator.

243
00:20:42,711 --> 00:20:44,303
Ahh... Huh?!

244
00:20:44,680 --> 00:20:46,341
Sorry Sasuke...

245
00:20:54,456 --> 00:20:55,514
Naruto!

246
00:20:58,027 --> 00:21:01,963
The password... I forgot it!

247
00:21:05,478 --> 00:21:10,074
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

248
00:21:10,183 --> 00:21:18,283
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

249
00:21:19,359 --> 00:21:27,892
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

250
00:21:28,501 --> 00:21:36,203
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

251
00:21:37,610 --> 00:21:43,139
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

252
00:21:43,216 --> 00:21:46,982
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

253
00:21:47,053 --> 00:21:50,614
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

254
00:21:51,091 --> 00:21:59,499
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

255
00:21:59,899 --> 00:22:04,962
<i>when you want to cry, and you want to run away</i>

256
00:22:05,038 --> 00:22:09,441
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

257
00:22:09,609 --> 00:22:13,272
<i>Just sing.</i>

258
00:22:13,580 --> 00:22:18,677
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

259
00:22:18,818 --> 00:22:20,945
<i>The two are one</i>

260
00:22:21,054 --> 00:22:27,323
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

261
00:22:27,927 --> 00:22:32,921
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

262
00:22:37,171 --> 00:22:38,536
Hey, hey, hey!

263
00:22:38,739 --> 00:22:43,176
It looks like you bullied
weaklings while I was gone.

264
00:22:43,477 --> 00:22:46,105
That explosion and
that huge snake,

265
00:22:46,180 --> 00:22:47,875
it's all your fault, isn't it?

266
00:22:48,315 --> 00:22:50,146
You damn snake bastard!

267
00:22:50,418 --> 00:22:55,412
Now that I, Naruto Uzumaki, is here,
I'll wipe the floor with you!

268
00:22:56,057 --> 00:22:59,322
Next episode: "Naruto's Counterattack:
Never Give In!"

269
00:22:59,694 --> 00:23:01,685
Look forward to my kicking butt!
